title: 820-00239-a spillage
message:
I have a liquid damaged board. 5v on usb meter  U2800 and U3100 were both bad so replaced them. I now have 20v 35ma. I only have 1v on PPBUS_G3H diode reading .395.
R7021/22 were both bad so replaced .
Q7030 pin1 = 20v, pin
